sections.text:
38-2912.Physical therapist, defined.

Physical therapist means a person licensed to practice physical therapy under the Physical Therapy Practice Act.

SourceLaws 2006, LB 994, § 130;R.S.Supp.,2006, § 71-1,374;Laws 2007, LB463, § 1005.
